<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heimeran von Haslang, Pfleger zu Hilpoltstein</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Rückgabe der sieben Pferde des Michael Rebel von Kemnath, Armmann von Anna und Hans Riegler, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_303" id="150v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_303_r2l27">Heymram <expan>haſling<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l28"><expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒum Stain </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_303_r2l29"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger vns hat fürgelegt fraw Anna des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l30">hanſen Ryglers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers eliche wirtin von Jren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l31">vnd <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> irs wirts wegen der <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> niht anheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l32">iſt . vvie daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">dem </del> vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> helffer dem Mıchel Rebel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l33">Jrem Armman von kemnaten den ſie mit tür vnd tor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l35">beſlieſſen vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>nÿmand<ex>en</ex></expan> anders . 
<del rend="strikethrough"> nehtein </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_303_r2l34">
<del rend="strikethrough">die <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht </del></ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l36"> <expan>Syb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> pferd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſchicken vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l37">
<del rend="strikethrough">wöllet / daʒ </del> <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Armman <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeine </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_303_r2l38">pferd wıderſchıcken wöllet / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_303" id="150v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heymram <expan>Hasling<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        czum Stain</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger, uns hat fürgelegt fraw Anna, des
                        Hansen Ryglers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers, eliche wirtin, von
                        iren und <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> irs wirts wegen, der
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> niht anheim ist, wie daz ir und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> helffer dem Michel Rebel, irem armman
                        von Kemnaten, den sie mit tür und tor besliessen und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>nymand<ex>en</ex></expan> anders,
                            <expan>syb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> pferd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> armman <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        seine pferd widerschicken wöllet. Als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
